<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>chinese on Steve's Blog</title><link>https://echowings.github.io/tags/chinese/</link><description>Recent content in chinese on Steve's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Aug 2021 21:51:14 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://echowings.github.io/tags/chinese/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to Batch Rename Filesname</title><link>https://echowings.github.io/p/how-to-batch-rename-filesname/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Aug 2021 21:51:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://echowings.github.io/p/how-to-batch-rename-filesname/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="how-to-batch-rename-filesname">How to batch rename filesname&lt;/h1>
